entries.femaleVariant: Their defenses are breached.
Johnny...
The path to the core lies open, but we don't have much time.
Got no idea either how this'll end. Thing is, wouldn't've ever got this far without you.
No idea if you got an ear out for me.
Might be better that way. This once you won't interrupt me mid-sentence, mid-thought.
Ancient fuckin' bastard…
Thanks... Thanks for everything.
Panam?
Adam Smasher.
Rogue…
Listen to me, you borged son of a bitch.
I'm going to miss that constant bickering, the unending fights.
I remember you. Promised to kill Silverhand once.
Silverhand sends his regards.
You killed a good man today.
Weighing if I should kill you or not.
Rogue finally smashed you, Smasher.
Gonna let you in on a little secret.
Was a good man, the guy you killed today.
Fifty years back, we killed in the name of all that was beautiful.
Rogue had it in for you – finally got what she wanted.
Saul didn't want to, but he followed me here. Made the ultimate sacrifice – for a friend, for family.
Somethin' you'll never understand.
Johnny? He's here with us. Now, he can't talk, but I can feel him under my skin.
In the end, gotcha – Silverhand triumphs.
entries.maleVariant: In the end, got you – Silverhand triumphs.

entries.femaleVariant: Rogue meant more than you or I ever could. Best there ever was. And you killed her.
Somethin' you'll never get.
Today, we can kill only in the name of those beautiful memories.
Shit, shit, shit!
You killed them! You borg fuck!
She knew the risks…
Silverhand – wanted to flatline 'im somethin' bad, didn'tcha? I mean, you swore you'd crush me.
Don't know shit, Smasher. She finished things off on her own terms.
What the fuck are you talking about?
He knew he was all-in.
A pussy always and forever.
You're talking tripe. I killed the old cunt.
Silverhand? How's this even possible?
We've come full circle. 'Cept back then, I'da finished you off 'thout a thought… Now?
You don't know shit. We've all changed. Yesterday's convictions mean nothing today.
You killed Rogue, you bastard.
Smasher, I remember you.
You in one piece?
[Pick up] Rogue, farewell…
Smasher, you fuckin' bastard…
You were… the best. Always.
I never knew an ox more stubborn… who'd follow family into fire.
And in the end did exactly that.
Me father always said that had he a desert isle to go to taking but one thing, he would take Rogue.
Their generation – made of a different mettle.
This is not the end! We'll meet again!
Doubt it.
Only human.
